        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2992661262" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16495473236744018031">Charming, moving, and soothing like the words of a friend. I don’t say this lightly...it’s easy to see why Ruskin Bond remains one of India’s most beloved writers. This book contains essays about his father, writing, walks in nature, windows with views, birds, favorite sounds, fragrant leaves, stamp collection, cherry trees, of living in various cities, so on and so forth. Each one is a delight. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


