  <span id="freeText10466650008877149021" style="display:none">📕Book : NOTES FROM A SMALL ROOM<br />🖍🖍Author : RUSKIN BOND<br />📚Publisher: PENGUIN BOOKS<br /><br />📙📙Ruskin Bond is undoubtedly one of the great and most loved authors in the country. He is my favourite author too.<br />‘’Wisdom does not come with age it is born with you in the cradle either you have it or you don’t.’’(Isn't it captivating?)<br /><br /> 📕🌟NOTES FROM A SMALL ROOM is an extraordinary book. Though notes are from a small room , they have a big impression on the reader’s mind. The content is mere not chapters, essays or articles but pure ecstasy. All the memories are giving a clear insight on how Ruskin Bond is inclined to nature and observe things minutely.These nostalgic compilations of Ruskin Bond have a lot of experience of his early life. All the articles are impressive, especially’ remember the day’, ‘letter to my father’,’ in search of the perfect window’ are dear to me.<br /><br />🌟How beautifully he sums up the book with the last content ‘thoughts on reaching 75’ One can self introspect after reading this.<br /><br />🌟Throughout the book, I was close to nature and found it pure ecstasy. Everyone can enjoy these precious notes in which he also shared his journey of becoming a writer and how he managed to earn money to follow his passion. <br /><br /> 🌟Out and out a masterpiece</span>
