<span id="freeTextContainer9202772110287494545">To delve into the mind of Ruskin Bond gives you an altogether brighter perspective to an otherwise dreary world. He inspires you to appreciate the smallest thing in the world to have faith in the beauty of nature. In this fast paced world, we forget to admire the night sky twinkling with stars or to see the rolling colours of the sky which change with every four hours of the day. Nothing I write can ever justify the feeling of actually reading those simple words describing the simplest thoughts </span>
  <span id="freeText9202772110287494545" style="display:none">To delve into the mind of Ruskin Bond gives you an altogether brighter perspective to an otherwise dreary world. He inspires you to appreciate the smallest thing in the world to have faith in the beauty of nature. In this fast paced world, we forget to admire the night sky twinkling with stars or to see the rolling colours of the sky which change with every four hours of the day. Nothing I write can ever justify the feeling of actually reading those simple words describing the simplest thoughts but which leave you with the most wonderful feeling in your heart.</span>
